{"tid":1847882,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"支幣太香！館長怒轟范瑋琪、小S：真他媽噁心","createTime":"2020-01-28T08:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T01:50:09.000Z","uid":32511,"like":733,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e0c034ad67164bf720215f6f590ffac7317141","tid":1847882,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:50:57.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，行政院長蘇貞昌禁止台灣口罩出口一個月，避免口罩缺貨讓國人恐慌。不過，藝人范瑋琪在私人臉書怒飆髒話，「我他X的有聽錯嗎？這個狗官算是個人嗎？」引起網友反彈。「館長」陳之漢則在臉書嗆爆：「看著那些中國台灣藝人，用口罩事件舔人民幣真他媽噁心～。」<br />\n <br />\n不只范瑋琪聲援中國，就連小S也在微博發聲：「我們都是人類，都住在這個地球上，如果不互相幫助，這不是人類該有的行爲吧！沒有愛，地球只會更糟！恨，比病毒還可怕！」現今兩人臉書湧入大批網友罵爆，館長也嗆說：「看著那些中國台灣藝人，用口罩事件舔人民幣真他媽噁心～。」<br />\n <br />\n不少網友認同館長說法，紛紛批說：「一堆貓哭耗子假慈悲的藝人」、「人民幣太香 不小心表態了」、「捐錢捐物資..人家飛彈還是對著你」。"},{"pid":"9a44b986fe723b554ef85a8bfb96c2a8c394ae4d","tid":1847882,"uid":331822,"like":245,"dislike":1,"score":244,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:51:31.000Z","msg":"真他媽噁心"},{"pid":"ac67364a3bf31f1decea421002ebee54c31fddd2","tid":1847882,"uid":337761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=d0cea79c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1221867978716844032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2